705374f-a.title: Brooklyn: Lafayette Avenue - Tompkins Avenue
705374f-a.text:
Lafayette Avenue, north sioe, between Tompkins anc Varcy Avenues.
View 1 shows the Hebrew.National school, at No. 687; view E, a
private mansion, at No. o7l.
